21:24.952 --> 21:26.995
Although, it can often lead
to disappointment.

21:27.079 --> 21:30.457
I have a lot to be getting on with today,
so if there's anything else you need--

21:30.541 --> 21:33.335
Yes. May I use
the little boy's room quickly?

21:34.878 --> 21:36.713
Top of the stairs,
second door on the left.

21:39.466 --> 21:41.301
