22:01.113 --> 22:03.532
- Yeah, it's all-- It's all great.
-<i>I told you you'd be next.</i>

22:03.615 --> 22:06.243
- Oh, shit. Are they still there?
-<i>It's all great.</i>

22:06.326 --> 22:09.204
-<i>Don't-- Don't panic because-- Yeah.</i>
- I'll-- I'll call you later.

22:09.288 --> 22:11.373
Hello. Oh, shit.

22:17.462 --> 22:18.922
