23:35.666 --> 23:36.917
Christ!

23:37.000 --> 23:39.169
- Oh, hello.
- Hi.

23:39.253 --> 23:40.254
Hey.

23:40.754 --> 23:43.465
These gentlemen are, just--

23:43.549 --> 23:48.136
