33:54.535 --> 33:56.078
Sorry, I just really need to pee.

33:56.161 --> 33:57.579
You do want
any of the one you brought?

33:57.663 --> 33:58.664
It will be--

34:07.965 --> 34:10.259
- Really?
- Yeah. I recommend it.

34:13.011 --> 34:18.225
It was in the 12 euros.

34:38.996 --> 34:40.289
Oh, God, that's disgusting.

35:03.896 --> 35:04.938
Yep.

