with the smaller ones.

35:33.842 --> 35:35.636
They're just adorable together.

35:42.601 --> 35:44.061
Right.

35:44.144 --> 35:46.855
Who wants some Easter flan,
courtesy of me?

35:46.939 --> 35:49.024
