while pulling your flies up?

35:52.611 --> 35:55.906
Have you washed your hands,
you dirty bitch?

35:55.989 --> 35:58.033
Of course, I washed my hands!

36:00.827 --> 36:02.996
- In the shape of a cross.
- Yeah.

36:03.080 --> 36:05.958
