36:07.835 --> 36:09.545
I've been sitting on that one forever.

36:11.046 --> 36:13.257
All your life.
I'm really glad you did.

36:13.340 --> 36:14.550
Come on.

36:22.057 --> 36:24.351
How long will it last? Till…

36:24.434 --> 36:26.687
It'll last about six months.

36:27.187 --> 36:29.731
I'm in. I love--
I love how there's never any…

36:29.815 --> 36:30.816
Come on, Bibi.

37:23.452 --> 37:25.787
Well, I told you there'd be eggs,
and now there's no baskets.

37:25.871 --> 37:27.831
- Molly, get-- get your coat, okay?
- What? Why?

37:27.915 --> 37:29.124
