so I just want to-- I want us to be there.

37:55.484 --> 37:57.319
- No, I don't.
- Will you close the door?

37:58.278 --> 38:01.240
Look, give--
give me a call when you-- Jesus.

38:01.323 --> 38:02.574
Take--

38:05.285 --> 38:06.662
Drive carefully!

38:10.082 --> 38:17.130
Pick up, pick up. Come on, come on.
