38:33.188 --> 38:35.607
Just, put some headphones
on your brother, Molly, and--

38:35.691 --> 38:39.570
Jesus! Jesus Christ, man!

38:41.405 --> 38:43.115
Jesus Christ, man.

38:43.198 --> 38:45.492
